Beautiful.

1760
01:26:12.041 --> 01:26:13.291
Thank you.

1761
01:26:13.916 --> 01:26:14.916
Thank you.

1762
01:26:19.458 --> 01:26:21.166
(RUMBLING. CRASHING)

1763
01:26:23.541 --> 01:26:26.250
Moonface. which way back to the Faraway Tree?

1764
01:26:27.416 --> 01:26:29.125
- Erm. right.
- JOE: Right!

1765
